With living costs rising, many are looking for ways to cut down, whether it's by replacing items like washing machines and cooking appliances or just by being more careful with the amount and frequency of usage. Find out how much energy your appliances use with one simple device. The Power Energy Meter features seven modes and can measure and display your voltage, current, energy, frequency, maximum current & power and total kWh.   The information given by the meterÂ can help you build a plan for saving money, allowing comparison between appliances, and you may even consider replacing some in favour of more energy-efficient versions.   